projects.name: Data privacy anonymization tool
projects.description: Developed a full stack tool for the Karnataka Police to anonymize Personally Identifiable Information (PII) in documents such as reports, ensuring data privacy. The tool uses an AI/ML model to identify and hide PII entities. Worked collaboratively with a team to execute the project, contributing to both frontend and backend development, and ensuring full stack integration.
